    <h3> A lot a people care about the stormwaters polution. People sometimes litter in the water that causes the water to get dirty. You can HELP by not littering. Here are some ways to not litter.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <img src="http://images.asianage.com/images/aa-Cover-9i8b7nr0na8ffa72nga89ucu13-20171119015245.Medi.jpeg">
    <br/>
    This is what happens when you burn garbage.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    1.
    <br/>
    While you are walking and you finished a drink, don't throw it to the street! If you can close it, close it, and then put it in a bag, nearby garbage, or in your jacket! I would think that this
    <br/>
    will work because the germs from the drink does not go down the drain.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    2.
    <br/>
    If you are in your car, and you have some garbage, better not to throw it out the window, keep it in your car until you are home. Sometimes people dump their drinks out their window!
    <br/>
    Many people throw their drink out of their window because not only they don't care, but also they're lazy, mad, stressed, or do not like the drink.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    3.
    <br/>
    Maybe this is rare but it could happen, burning garbage. That is a bad thing that could happen because the fumes from the burned garbage can go to the air, or into someones body. If you have
    <br/>
    If you do have trash in your house and you like burning things, don't burn garbage because the smoke can cause asthma attacks, health problems and accidental fires.
